## Esna 457 {-}

- Location: Top of column C
- Date: Vespasian
- [Hieroglyphic Text](https://www.ifao.egnet.net/uploads/publications/enligne/Temples-Esna004.pdf#page=129){target="_blank"}  
  
Vespasian is beloved of:  
  
**South**  Shemanefer   
**East**  Neith   
**North**  Menhyt    
**West**  Menehwy
